                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><div style='background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;' class='serif serif-md'><a href='/lifegroups/girls-night-out/'><img src='/site/assets/files/1081/14164315519_1600.640x360.jpg' class=' img-responsive img-full-width' /></a><div style='padding:10px 20px;'> <h3 style='margin-top:0px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:6px;'><a href='/lifegroups/girls-night-out/'>Girls Night Out</a></h3>Ladies you are invited to join us on the 1st Monday of each month at 6:30 pm. We meet at different restaurants in the community and enjoy each other’s company. Contact Terri Shields at (812)890-1493 for the location of our next meeting. We...<div class='clearfix'></div><div class='mg-t-md mg-b-sm'><a href='/lifegroups/girls-night-out/' class='btn btn-left btn-default'><i class='icon-right-4'></i> Read More</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><div style='background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;' class='serif serif-md'><a href='/lifegroups/mens-group/'><img src='/site/assets/files/1081/14164315519_1600.640x360.jpg' class=' img-responsive img-full-width' /></a><div style='padding:10px 20px;'> <h3 style='margin-top:0px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:6px;'><a href='/lifegroups/mens-group/'>Men&#039;s Group</a></h3>Pastor Dave Dunbar sends out a weekly devotion via text message. If you’d like to receive the devotion or for more information about Men’s Group events, contact Pastor Dave at 812-403-3817.<div class='clearfix'></div><div class='mg-t-md mg-b-sm'><a href='/lifegroups/mens-group/' class='btn btn-left btn-default'><i class='icon-right-4'></i> Read More</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><div style='background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;' class='serif serif-md'><a href='/lifegroups/youth-group/'><img src='/site/assets/files/1081/14164315519_1600.640x360.jpg' class=' img-responsive img-full-width' /></a><div style='padding:10px 20px;'> <h3 style='margin-top:0px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:6px;'><a href='/lifegroups/youth-group/'>Youth Group</a></h3>If you’re in 6th grade through high school, we want to invite you to youth group! We meet upstairs on Sundays from 6-7pm. Come enjoy good eats, great company, plenty of laughter, and great discussion! If you need a ride or have questions about...<div class='clearfix'></div><div class='mg-t-md mg-b-sm'><a href='/lifegroups/youth-group/' class='btn btn-left btn-default'><i class='icon-right-4'></i> Read More</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><div style='background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;' class='serif serif-md'><a href='/lifegroups/sermon-study-notes/'><img src='/site/assets/files/1081/14164315519_1600.640x360.jpg' class=' img-responsive img-full-width' /></a><div style='padding:10px 20px;'> <h3 style='margin-top:0px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:6px;'><a href='/lifegroups/sermon-study-notes/'>Sermon Study Notes</a></h3>Every week on Tuesdays from 5:30-6:30 pm, we meet to study and discuss the weekly Sermon Study Notes. The notes can be found in the worship folder. It’s a great time to dig in and learn more about God’s Word and meet some great people. We...<div class='clearfix'></div><div class='mg-t-md mg-b-sm'><a href='/lifegroups/sermon-study-notes/' class='btn btn-left btn-default'><i class='icon-right-4'></i> Read More</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><div style='background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;' class='serif serif-md'><a href='/lifegroups/coffee-talk/'><img src='/site/assets/files/1081/14164315519_1600.640x360.jpg' class=' img-responsive img-full-width' /></a><div style='padding:10px 20px;'> <h3 style='margin-top:0px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:6px;'><a href='/lifegroups/coffee-talk/'>Coffee Talk</a></h3>Enjoy a great cup of coffee and a devotional with wonderful ladies on Fridays from 10-11 am in the Prayer Room at Thursday Church (218 Main St.) All ladies are welcome! Contact Angie Warmuth at (812)887-8426 with any questions.<div class='clearfix'></div><div class='mg-t-md mg-b-sm'><a href='/lifegroups/coffee-talk/' class='btn btn-left btn-default'><i class='icon-right-4'></i> Read More</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><div style='background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;' class='serif serif-md'><a href='/lifegroups/adult-coloring-group/'><img src='/site/assets/files/1081/14164315519_1600.640x360.jpg' class=' img-responsive img-full-width' /></a><div style='padding:10px 20px;'> <h3 style='margin-top:0px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:6px;'><a href='/lifegroups/adult-coloring-group/'>Adult coloring group</a></h3>Enjoy a familiar pastime with a great group of adults. We meet on Mondays from 6-7 pm (excluding the 1st Monday of the month) in the Prayer Room at Thursday Church (218 Main St.). Supplies are provided! All adults are welcome! Call Renee with any...<div class='clearfix'></div><div class='mg-t-md mg-b-sm'><a href='/lifegroups/adult-coloring-group/' class='btn btn-left btn-default'><i class='icon-right-4'></i> Read More</a></div></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4"><div style='background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;' class='serif serif-md'><a href='/lifegroups/healing-hearts-grief-recovery/'><img src='/site/assets/files/1081/14164315519_1600.640x360.jpg' class=' img-responsive img-full-width' /></a><div style='padding:10px 20px;'> <h3 style='margin-top:0px;padding-top:6px;padding-bottom:6px;'><a href='/lifegroups/healing-hearts-grief-recovery/'>Healing Hearts Grief Recovery</a></h3>Offering support as you find physical, emotional, and spiritual healing and hope. The book is available at The Bible Book Store (106 Main St., Vincennes) for $11.97. Sundays from 3:30-5:30pm at Thursday Church, (218 Main Street) in the Prayer...<div class='clearfix'></div><div class='mg-t-md mg-b-sm'><a href='/lifegro